{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nExperience the Lagoon 46 “Mple” – Your Luxury Catamaran Adventure in Greece\n\nStep aboard the breathtaking Lagoon 46 “Mple,” a luxury catamaran that seamlessly combines style, comfort, and top-tier functionality, making it the ideal choice for an unforgettable yachting adventure in Greece. Designed for seafarers who crave sophistication and exploration, this catamaran offers a harmonious blend of cutting-edge innovation and timeless elegance.\n\nLuxury Meets Comfort\nThe meticulously designed interior of “Mple” invites you to unwind in a space where contemporary aesthetics meet ultimate comfort. The expansive salon, adorned with panoramic windows, creates a seamless connection with the stunning Greek seascape while offering a serene haven for relaxation. With accommodations for up to 8 guests in four spacious cabins, each with a private en-suite bathroom, “Mple” guarantees unparalleled comfort and privacy for your charter experience.\n\nOutdoor Opulence at Its Finest\nThe Lagoon 46 “Mple” takes outdoor luxury to new heights. The flybridge, equipped with sunbathing areas and premium entertainment facilities, is the perfect spot to soak up the Mediterranean sun or enjoy sunset cocktails. The spacious deck areas ensure everyone has their own slice of paradise to relax and enjoy the views of Greece’s iconic coastline, crystal-clear waters, and hidden coves.\n\nA Symphony of Sailing Excellence\n“Mple” is not just about luxury; it’s a sailing masterpiece. Its state-of-the-art technology and nautical finesse deliver a smooth and exhilarating sailing experience. Whether you’re navigating the serene waters of the Cyclades, exploring the historic Ionian Islands, or anchoring in a secluded bay, “Mple” promises a journey that is both thrilling and tranquil.\n\nWhy Charter in Greece with Lagoon 46 “Mple”?\nDiscover the unmatched beauty of Greece aboard “Mple,” your gateway to an extraordinary maritime escapade. Ideal for families, friends, or romantic getaways, this catamaran offers the perfect balance of adventure and relaxation. From sun-kissed beaches to ancient ruins, every moment aboard “Mple” is an invitation to explore the wonders of the Aegean and beyond.\n\nEmbark on a yacht charter in Greece like no other. The Lagoon 46 “Mple” is your ultimate partner for a luxurious and unforgettable sailing holiday. Book now to experience the perfect blend of oceanic beauty, first-class indulgence, and the magic of Greece.","blueprint":{"name":"MPLE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::accb4be0-4132-11f0-bced-d750775c38db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::aca5e990-4132-11f0-bced-d750775c38db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::aca30360-4132-11f0-bced-d750775c38db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::acbf3df1-4132-11f0-bced-d750775c38db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::accaafa0-4132-11f0-849f-5bc6752f2654/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::ac921370-4132-11f0-9d61-73838709c07a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::aca1cae0-4132-11f0-849f-5bc6752f2654/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::ac9791b0-4132-11f0-849f-5bc6752f2654/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::aca685d0-4132-11f0-9d61-73838709c07a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::87b38cb0-f038-11ee-abef-cf22b0fc9a07::assets::acbf3df0-4132-11f0-bced-d750775c38db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::v